# **6. NGE to the Left**

### **Logic**

- Traverse left \u2192 right  
- Maintain decreasing stack  

### **Implementation**

```cpp
vector<int> ngeLeft(vector<int> &a) {
    int n = a.size();
    vector<int> ans(n, -1);
    stack<int> st;

    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        while (!st.empty() && st.top() <= a[i])
            st.pop();

        if (!st.empty())
            ans[i] = st.top();

        st.push(a[i]);
    }
    return ans;
}
```

